ðŸ“Œ Initial API List for Milestone 1
------------------------------------

++++Overview++++++

Features covered:

. Register/Login system

. Manual income/expense entry

. Basic dashboard

*********ðŸ”‘ Authentication APIs************

1. User Registration
 . POST /api/auth/register

. Body: { name, email, password }

. Response: { success, userId, token }

2.User Login

. POST /api/auth/login

. Body: { email, password }

. Response: { success, token, userId }

3. Get User Profile (after login)

. GET /api/auth/me

. Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>

. Response: { userId, name, email }

***********ðŸ’° Income & Expense APIs***************

4. Add Transaction (income/expense)

. POST /api/transactions

$. Body: { type: "income" | "expense", amount, category, date, note }

$. Response: { success, transactionId }

5. Fetch Transactions (list view)

$. GET /api/transactions?from=YYYY-MM-DD&to=YYYY-MM-DD

$. Response: [ { transactionId, type, amount, category, date, note } ]

***************ðŸ“Š Dashboard APIs*******************
6. Fetch Dashboard Summary

GET /api/dashboard/summary

Response:

{
  "totalIncome": 12000,
  "totalExpense": 8000,
  "balance": 4000,
  "recentTransactions": [
    { "id": 1, "type": "income", "amount": 5000, "date": "2025-09-01" },
    { "id": 2, "type": "expense", "amount": 2000, "date": "2025-09-02" }
  ]
}


